from numpy.random import randint

counts = hc_train4.select('label').groupBy('label').count().collect()

#print(higherBound)

hc_train4 = hc_train4.withColumn("randIndex", udfRandGen("label"))
df_subsample = hc_train4.filter(hc_train4['randIndex'] < TRESHOLD_TO_FILTER)
df_subsample = df_subsample.drop('randIndex')

print("Distribution of Pos and Neg cases of the down-sampled training data are: \n", df_subsample.groupBy("label").count().take(3))
